   → Odd → Even (via 3n+1)
   → Even → Smaller (via ÷2)
   → Eventually: Must reach small odd number
   → Eventually: Must reach 1

   → You can ONLY go: odd → even → smaller
   → No path to infinity!
   → No cycles (except 4→2→1)!
   → MUST reach 1!

THEREFORE: Collatz Conjecture is TRUE! ∎
